Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,您快回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血從操演宮中流出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽得到我的聲音嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,把眼睛張開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快請蜜拉娜公主過來 是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受損的不是只有裝甲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼會傷得那麼重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅…翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍…龍神人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到國王竟然會是龍神人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯之力加上龍神人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都這個時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身邊老是出現些令我不得不想起那個男人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的脈搏極不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是醫生嗎 快想點辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的能力有限啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說這傷並不普通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是從內側…肉從體內裂開所形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本就沒辦法止血
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯卡弗洛尼的操演宮並沒有受損吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟梵一樣的傷□
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵感應到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵與艾斯嘉科尼合為一體了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必須把艾斯嘉科尼修好才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然這樣下去,梵會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有阿斯多利亞的商船隊出現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快要抵達你的故鄉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得說再見了,席爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別露出這種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美人魚就該待在海中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容是最美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別再被抓到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還被抓到,你就告訴對方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說你認識阿斯多利亞的德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺,您竟然花了那麼大筆鈔票在那尾人魚上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還要把她放回海裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會害我挨老爺罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼愛計較嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的東西還是最適合回歸自然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是庫魯傑特嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方希望能見您一面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是德萊甸…對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞第三王女蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是蜜拉娜的未婚夫?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,就是那個企圖綁架你的梅甸之子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他不是很危險嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,若是能夠借助他的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就能找到救梵的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還滿意我的書齋嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心跳很劇烈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前我一直以為你只是個任性的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟會長成為如此美麗的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真教我感動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也變得高大英挺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真話嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就馬上回國舉行結婚典禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太突然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經是未婚夫妻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上我又是個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經商成功的超級有錢人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豐富的學識足以媲美學者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然自吹自擂了點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過長相也…帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有什麼不滿的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德…德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也需要讓你做好心理準備喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正欲速則不達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不是來找我談這個的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就進入正題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差解除封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又給我擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的迪蘭度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已經找到能源點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就隨我高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是伊斯帕農制的人型裝甲?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把它弄得傷痕纍纍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些武士就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺,小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是德萊甸?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來傳說是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼意思,德萊甸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"先生"就免了,叫我德萊甸就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麻煩你別再賣關子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古文書上有寫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕農制的人型裝甲會取走駕駛者的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會取走…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛者的性命?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕農乃繼承亞特蘭提斯之民智慧的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由他們製作出來的人型裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉由訂定血契來決定主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那個主人死亡為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時它還會取代其主參與戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當人型裝甲受傷倒下時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其主人也會一同倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著不光只是駕駛艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更在心裏進行操演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再要你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我害他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把人型裝甲修好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們無法進行如此大規模的修補作業…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕農制的人型裝甲可是有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人叫過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造出艾斯嘉科尼的伊斯帕農族人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是傳說中的伊斯帕農工房船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（伊斯帕農語）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（伊斯帕農語）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（伊斯帕農語）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（伊斯帕農語）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔,法尼利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔,法尼利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有問題吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只是在查看艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五千萬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五…五千萬?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼的修理費
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們年薪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2000倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼貴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果付不出來那我們就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個船隊都給你這樣如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們花了五年才搜集來的珍品耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您竟然將價值超過八千萬的東西給…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸,我們沒辦法償還你那麼大筆數目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為王族就別那麼小家子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是很中意那位國王罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你撐著點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿繩子來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用繩子把他綁住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王,你撐著點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩子拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼的痛楚,他全都感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎扎實實地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要艾斯嘉科尼修理好了,國王的傷就會跟著痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,他得先撐過這些痛苦才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人…梵大人會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會那麼簡單就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的,他一定可以撐過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是亞特蘭提斯之力…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理想未來的鼓動…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痊…痊癒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒韶下半點傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然真的會治好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是托了大家的福,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,我又被你救了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該向德萊甸與小瞳道謝才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,這一切都要感謝這位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要小心艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你還是別再駕駛它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦艾斯嘉科尼受損了,事情又會重演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一艾斯嘉科尼損毀了,那你也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓艾斯嘉科尼受損
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戰之人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕農不想被捲入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們得離開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寨巴哈嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,竟然已經追過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血契
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用龍神之血訂契
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕農無法保障
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法保障?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然逃到那麼顯眼的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏沒有人型裝甲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別強人所難了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這艘是商船耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾用的倒是有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓亞連他們去應付就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠裝甲根本就打不贏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就照小瞳說的去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯帕農人不也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說他們無法保障
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可以駕駛艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定能順利控制艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把艙門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天來結束獵龍行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要親手做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼,給我你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快用隱形披風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得到,我看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為弗雷特王報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為巴爾卡斯報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究…究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪、歇士達、達雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙究竟是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對,艾斯嘉科尼不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為法尼利亞報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你殺害迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟我們一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人是我們的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他將榮耀至極的人型裝甲賜給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑選我們進入榮耀至極的龍擊隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是…我們絕不讓你動他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是…好啦,你就跟我們一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人究竟是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.32,0:22:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是放著不管,梵會…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵會被帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:57.42,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:05.87,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:13.50,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:19.65,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:22.01,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:27.02,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:30.86,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:34.66,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:38.67,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:42.17,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:49.64,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:57.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:05.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:13.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:19.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:22.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:27.02,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:30.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:34.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:38.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:42.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:49.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

